Skills, an Overview and Retrospective                           Chapter 3

These types of skills concerning spellcraft are known in the world:

Form skills:
   * Transmutation   Changing one object into another, forever.
   * Illusion        Casting deceiving spells, optical trickery.
   * Divination      Calling upon the Deities.
   * Enchantment     Changing the state of an object or person temporarily.
   * Conjuration     Summoning objects or creatures from apparently nowhere.
   * Abjuration      Destructing effects or objects by spellcraft.

Elemental skills:  Typical ingredients you learn to control:
   * Fire             Coal, magma-rocks, fire-gems, fosfor.  
   * Air              Bubbles, feathers.
   * Earth            Rocks, gems, slabs, mud.
   * Water            Mud, potions, fluids.
   * Life             Flowers, mushrooms, animals.
   * Death            Corpses, black gems, skeletons.
